## ğŸ›¡ï¸ Trusted Framework Tokens

Automatically recognized as protected:
- `sesskey` (Moodle)
- `authenticity_token` (Rails)
- `csrfmiddlewaretoken` (Django)
- `__RequestVerificationToken` (ASP.NET)
- `_token` (Laravel)

